? AGNICART equipment will be featured in next upcoming movie "BHOOMI" releaseing on Pongal 2021. In this movie ACTOR JAYAM RAVI will drive AGNICART''s 5row cultivator using native breed "Kangayam bullock".
? Received FICCI, Madurai for best Startup award for modernization of agriculture.
? Received Carbon Zero Challenge award - 2023 by IIT Madras for best technology benefitting small and medium farmers.
? Received RKVY Grant of 25,00,000 Lakhs for scaling the cart across states.
? Received EDI IVP Grant 2 Lakhs for design and development of Wet Land plowing. Agnicarts Agri Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India Tamil Nadu, India Andhra Pradesh, India', '{"organization_name":"Agnicarts","organization_code":"AGNIC1723273439062"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
insert into public.innovation_guild_vendors (portal_vendor_id, vendor_name, about_vendor, website_details, location_text, city, state, country, service_locations, tags, portal_vendor_link, portal_contact_name, portal_email, portal_phone, website_email, website_phone, website_address, final_contact_email, final_contact_phone, final_contact_address, contact_source_url, website_status, legacy_products_links, contact_notes, latitude, longitude, products_count, search_text, raw_vendor, synced_at, updated_at) values ('AGRIL1764931859632', 'Agrilectric Private Limited', 'Agrilectric Private Limited is an agri-technology enterprise focused on developing electric and smart farm mechanization solutions for small and marginal farmers in India. The company aims to reduce farmers'' dependence on fuel-powered equipment by offering low-operating-cost, low-maintenance, and environmentally sustainable alternatives.
Agrilectric designs and manufactures electric agricultural implements that improve productivity while lowering operational expenses, noise, emissions, and physical fatigue. With a strong focus on affordability, usability, and after-sales support, the enterprise addresses real on-ground challenges faced by farmers across diverse crop systems and terrains.
The company''s mission is to make clean, efficient, and accessible farm mechanization available to every farmer, supporting sustainable agriculture and long-term rural impact.', null, 'No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India | Karnataka, India', null, null, 'India', '{"No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India","Karnataka, India"}', '{"Harvesting","Weeding","Agriculture","Maintenance and management"}', 'https://innovationguild.in/innovation/home', 'Agrilectric Private Limited', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India', 'https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4330/electric-brush-cutter-e-brush-cutter', 'Innovation Guild API does not expose organization website/email/phone', 'https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4330/electric-brush-cutter-e-brush-cutter', 'Address captured from Innovation Guild. Email and phone can be enriched later through organization-contact-seed.json and admin syncs.', 13.1151600552861, 77.50414697528532, 1, 'Electric Brush Cutter (e-Brush Cutter) The e-Brush Cutter is a multi-purpose electric agricultural implement designed to replace conventional petrol engine brush cutters with a cleaner, quieter, and more economical solution. It is suitable for daily farm operations including harvesting, weeding, pruning, raking, and landscaping.
Technical Specifications:
Rated Power: 2 kW electric motor
Maximum Speed: 6500 RPM
Battery Pack: 48 V, 15 Ah
Backup Time: Up to 180 minutes (depending on attachment)
Charging Time: 2 hours (fast charger optional)
Tube Diameter: 28 mm | Shaft Diameter: 8 mm
Weight: 11.25 kg
Performance & Operations:
The system can perform all operations typically handled by engine-based brush cutters, delivering consistent power with very low vibration and near-silent operation.
Cost & Sustainability:
Operating cost of approximately &#8377;1.8 - &#8377;2 per hour
Near-zero maintenance due to absence of fuel, oil, and engine components
Zero emissions and low noise, making it environmentally friendly and safer for operators
The e-Brush Cutter is designed for small and marginal farmers seeking a reliable, low-cost, and sustainable alternative to fuel-powered farm equipment. Agrilectric Private Limited Harvesting Weeding No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India Karnataka, India', '{"organization_name":"Agrilectric Private Limited","organization_code":"AGRIL1764931859632"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
