By cutting fuel and maintenance costs by over 80% and reducing harvesting effort and cost by up to 90%, it offers a clean, affordable alternative to traditional machines. HV Electric Vehicle Pvt. Ltd. Harvesting Nayara Petrol Pump, 148, Sehore - Bhopal Rd, Kopal, Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh 462044, India Madhya Pradesh, India', '{"organization_name":"HV Electric Vehicle Pvt. Ltd.","organization_code":"HV_EL1767092278396"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
