animal-deterrent-device', 'Innovation Guild API does not expose organization website/email/phone', 'https://innovationguild.in/innovation/5236/pb-v-30-solar-powered-autonomous-wild-animal-deterrent-device', 'Address captured from Innovation Guild. Email and phone can be enriched later through organization-contact-seed.json and admin syncs.', 12.9628669, 77.57750899999999, 1, 'PB v 3.0 Solar powered Autonomous wild animal deterrent device Parabraksh, a Solar-Powered Wild Animal Deterrent System, is an innovative solution designed&#10;to protect farmlands and sensitive areas from animal intrusions. Using advanced solar technology&#10;
and an illusion of moving flashing LED lights, Parabraksh creates a psychological barrier that&#10;
keeps animals away without causing them harm. Its eco-friendly and low-maintenance design&#10;
