s. Also weeding machinery is having multiple attachments. Along with weeding attachment fertiliser sowing adjustment is also provided. Maa Vaishnav Rani Engineering Works, Wadhona, Maharashtra Sowing Bed making Weeding Wadhona, Maharashtra, India Maharashtra, India', '{"organization_name":"Maa Vaishnav Rani Engineering Works, Wadhona, Maharashtra","organization_code":"MAA_V1767961085258"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
