https://innovationguild.in/innovation/1353/heliot-smart-irrigation-system', 'Address captured from Innovation Guild. Email and phone can be enriched later through organization-contact-seed.json and admin syncs.', 17.4813993, 78.44899350000001, 3, 'HELIOT Automatic Weather Station – AI Powered SMART ENVIRO SENSE HELIOT SMART ENVIRO SENSE is an IoT-enabled, solar-powered Automatic Weather Station (AWS) designed for village-level microclimate monitoring and climate-smart agriculture. Developed by Navariti Innovation Pvt Ltd under the HELIOT.AI brand, this solution provides real-time weather data, localized 8-day forecasts, AI-based crop advisory, irrigation recommendations, fertilizer guidance, and pest & disease alerts.
The system measures key weather parameters including temperature, humidity, atmospheric pressure, rainfall, wind speed & direction, solar radiation, and other customizable sensors based on project requirements. It is built for deployment in plains, hilly terrains, tribal areas, high-value crop clusters, and rural communities.
The "One Village - One Weather Station" model ensures accurate village-level data instead of district-level approximations. Farmers receive crop-stage specific advisory through the HELIOT analytics platform via real-time dashboards and mobile access.
Key Benefits:
10 - 20% Yield Increase
20 - 40% Water Savings
Improved fertilizer efficiency
Early pest & disease warning
Climate risk preparedness
Better crop planning & harvest scheduling
The system supports FPOs, NGOs, CSR projects, agricultural universities, and rural development agencies in driving climate resilience and sustainable agriculture.
HELIOT AWS is currently deployed across multiple Indian states including Telangana, Maharashtra, Andhra Pradesh, Karnataka, Rajasthan, and others, enabling data-driven decision making for small and marginal farmers. NAVARITI INNOVATION PVT LTD climate advisory  Data analytics  Weather monitoring Balanagar, Hyderabad, Telangana, India Maharashtra, India Odisha, India Andhra Pradesh, India Karnataka, India Telangana, India Rajasthan, India Tamil Nadu, India HELIOT Smart Irrigation Controller (Motor Control System) HELIOT Smart Irrigation Controller is an AI and IoT-enabled motor automation system designed to optimize irrigation management for farmers. Developed by Navariti Innovation Pvt Ltd under the HELIOT.AI brand, the system allows farmers to operate irrigation pumps and valves remotely using a mobile application.
The controller enables automatic ON/OFF operation, timer-based scheduling, soil moisture-based automation, and real-time motor monitoring. It includes protection features such as phase failure detection, dry-run protection, and voltage fluctuation safeguards to ensure motor safety and long operational life.
Farmers can operate motors from anywhere, reducing repeated farm visits and saving time, water, and electricity. The system integrates with HELIOT''s weather station and advisory platform to provide irrigation recommendations based on crop stage, weather forecast, and soil conditions.
Key Features:
Remote motor ON/OFF via mobile app
Timer & scheduling mode
Manual & automatic mode
Phase failure detection
Dry-run protection
Voltage fluctuation protection
Soil moisture-based irrigation (optional)
Real-time motor & power status monitoring
Water & electricity savings (20 - 40%)
User-friendly mobile app interface
Impact:
Reduced water wastage
Reduced electricity consumption
Improved crop consistency
Reduced labor & travel cost
Better irrigation scheduling
Increased productivity
The solution is suitable for small, marginal, and commercial farmers growing field crops, horticulture crops, and plantations. Irrigation IOT based motor automation Precision agriculture  HELIOT Smart Irrigation System The HELIOT Smart Irrigation System offers smallholder farmers an affordable, IoT and AI-driven solution to optimize agricultural practices. Benefits include enhanced crop yields, efficient water usage, and reduced manual labor. With features like automatic irrigation controllers, temperature, and humidity control, wireless control, a valve control system, and a mobile app & dashboard interface. Farmers can enhance their yields efficiently designed for small and marginal farmers, it minimizes human intervention. Smart Irrigation Bhavana Enclave, Amar Jyoti Colony, Anand Nagar, Bowenpally, Secunderabad, Telangana 500011, India', '{"organization_name":"NAVARITI INNOVATION PVT LTD","organization_code":"NAVAR1723445963240"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
