https://innovationguild.in/innovation/5067/turmeric-polish-machine', 'Address captured from Innovation Guild. Email and phone can be enriched later through organization-contact-seed.json and admin syncs.', 18.8450281, 78.6353199, 3, 'Coconut shredding machine Lot of Coconut shells are piles up in the dump yards with the lack of awareness in creating valuable products from the waste coconut shells.There are large coconut processing units in the cities but all the coconuts in the tier 2 and tier 3 cities are piles up in the dump yards, so considering the environment pollution and value addition to the coconut shells.
we have designed a Compact coconut shredding machine, which runs with single phase 3 Hp motor and can be used in every rural village where all the coconuts in their village can be transformed to coco fibre and coco peat which has lot of demand in the current market.
This machine eradicates the pollution and creates employment and the bi products can be sold in their nearby villages or in the E commerce platforms. Prabhath Industries Bed making Prabhath Industries, RJVP+VJ5 Tata Showroom Back Side, 2-67, Nizamabad - Koratla Rd, Mahalaxmi Nagar Colony, Metpally, Telangana 505325, India Tamil Nadu, India Telangana, India Andhra Pradesh, India Karnataka, India Turmeric Boiling Unit Typically Turmeric is boiled in the water with the help of Huge containers and boilers, farmers struggle a lot to boil water and transfer the hot turmeric from the boiler, the water used in the boiling unit absorbs most of the minerals and important qualities of turmeric in the process, So i have designed a Turmeric boiling Cooker which cooks the turmeric with the help of steam and not immersed in the water, Thus the water intake in the boiling will be less and the turmeric circumin levels will be maintained properly and the pressurised steam helps to cook the turmeric quickly compared to traditional Cooking methods. 6VGVGVJJ+6C Turmeric Polish Machine Turmeric polishing is a major task in the processing system, There are Tractor operated heavy duty polish machines available in the market but they are not affordable for the farmers with less crop and poor farmers, So i have designed various capacities of Turmeric polish machines which starts from 25 Kg, 35 Kg, 50 Kg, 100 Kg and 200 Kg which are completely operated with Induction motor. and It is easy to operate by farmers and workers. It takes 35-40 Minutes to polish the turmeric. Drying 1-6-110/1, Mahalaxmi Nagar Colony, Metpally, Telangana 505325, India', '{"organization_name":"Prabhath Industries","organization_code":"PRABH1761808480582"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
