nt, and user-friendly solution for managing weed growth in paddy fields. It supports farmers in maintaining healthy crops and improving yield while reducing the physical strain of manual weeding. Tamil Nadu, India Meghalaya, India e-Kunte Poultry Raking Machine(Battery Powered) A Battery-powered Poultry Raking machine is designed to maintain optimal conditions in poultry farms. It aids in managing litter by evenly distributing it, preventing the buildup of harmful substances by daily raking and promoting a healthier environment for the birds with an adjustable raking mechanism covering up to 3ft and easily operable by any individual. Raking e-Kunte Single Wheel Single Row Weeder (Battery Powered) The Single-wheel Single-row Weeder is a Battery-powered Weeding implement engineered to streamline intercrop activities like Removing Weeds, Ridging, and Intercultivation in a single row of crops. Designed with efficiency and ease of use, women-friendly, this innovative implement is an essential companion for farmers seeking to maintain weed-free fields without extensive labor. e-Kunte Trolley Brush Cutter(Battery Powered) Trolley Brush Cutter is a versatile and eco-friendly solution designed to cut off dense Weeds with ease at the plantations. Powered by batteries, this brush cutter offers convenient operation without the hassle of vibrations, fuel or emissions, making it an ideal choice for avoiding Weedicides. Mounted on trolley wheels which makes it easy to move around in the plantation e-Trolley (Battery Powered) E-Trolley is a robust, Battery-powered transport solution designed to enhance efficiency in agricultural operations. With its high-capacity Battery and sturdy construction, it effortlessly navigates through rough terrains, carrying heavy loads such as harvested crops, tools, soil, fertilizers and other input supplies within the plantations. Transportation Electric Paddy Thresher (Battery powered ) Battery Powered paddy thresher is a tool designed for threshing