 afford machine tools for their small land, Tools we have designed are perfect match for the farmers need, it doesn''t require maintained, It''s light weight and durable, specially designed for all genders. Mitti Dhan Weeding Agriculture Production Valsad, Gujarat, India Gujarat, India Year Launched 2020 Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services yes Spare Parts for Product yes Demo Installations yes Engine Details Test Opportunity Support Not listed Suitable Crops Test Imported Parts No Network Distributors none Suitable Soil Test Power Source Manual Number of Unit Installed Not listed Product Dimensions Test Technical Training yes Minimum cost of product 300 Weather Conditions Test Product Weight Test Performance Parameters Test Product Attachments Test Opportunity Stage Idea Financing Support open Other Conditions Test Suitable Terrains Test Maximum cost of product 500', '{"innovation_id":"1351","slug":"efficient-and-low-cost-weeding-tool","title":"Efficient and Low Cost Weeding Tool","description":"Weeding tools are either machine operated or a simple sickle, while using sickle it gives back and knee pain and it''s very time consuming work, Small farmers can''t afford machine tools for their small land, Tools we have designed are perfect match for the farmers need, it doesn''t require maintained, It''s light weight and durable, specially designed for all genders.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/1351/efficient-and-low-cost-weeding-tool","organization_name":"Mitti Dhan","organization_code":"MITTI1723444744009","organization_description":"Our mission is to empower the rural community by offering trainings, workshops and demonstrations in various topics and vocations, for the support a self-sustaining and ecologically-viable local economy. Such topics include women''s health and empowerment (smokeless chula, ergonomically-designed hand tools, basic literacy, and hygiene); youth (vocational training in both modern and traditional technologies; rural employment, games and activities, and guidance and mentorship); children (games and activities, language classes, traditional arts and crafts, and connecting to nature through farming and nature walks); and topics and gatherings for men (eco-friendly and low-cost construction techniques, farming technologies and rural innovations, organic farming techniques, seed exchanges, renewable energy and appropriate technologies, water conservation technologies, etc.).","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.PRODUCTION"],"subcategories":["Production"],"tag_codes":[],"tags":["Weeding"],"stage":"Idea","minimum_cost":"300","maximum_cost":"500","power_source":"Manual","year_launched":"2020","primary_location":"Valsad, Gujarat, India","location_text":"Valsad, Gujarat, India | Gujarat, India","locations":["Valsad, Gujarat, India","Gujarat, India"],"latitude":20.5992349,"longitude":72.9342451,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1723444508074-Weeder_-_Hiren_Panchal.png","image_urls":["https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1723444508074-Weeder_-_Hiren_Panchal.png","https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_design_gallery/1723444709962-Weeder_-_Hiren_Panchal.png"],"videos":[{"source_url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-d5k_nSJhsw","embed_url":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-d5k_nSJhsw","platform":"youtube"},{"source_url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KQpSat7SgS0","embed_url":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KQpSat7SgS0","platform":"youtube"}],"specifications":[{"key":"Year Launched","value":"2020","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.YEAR_LAUNCHED"},{"key":"Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services","value":"yes","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.TRAINING_ON_MAINTENANCE_AND_AFTER_SALES_SERVICES"},{"key":"Spare Parts for Pr