The e-Brush Cutter is designed for small and marginal farmers seeking a reliable, low-cost, and sustainable alternative to fuel-powered farm equipment. Agrilectric Private Limited Harvesting Weeding Agriculture Maintenance and management No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India Karnataka, India Weather Conditions Works efficiently in dry and moderately moist field conditions. Performs best when soil is not fully water-logged. Electric drive ensures smooth operation in hot and humid climates with minimal performance loss. No fuel-evaporation issues during summer and no cold-start problems in winter. Suitable Crops Paddy, Wheat, Arecanut, Coconut, Millets, Maize, Groundnut, Vegetables (Tomato, Chilli, Brinjal, Beans), Plantation crops, Horticulture crops, Inter-row crops, Fodder grass, Dry leaves & mulch residue, Paddy straw, Coconut fronds. Demo Installations yes Imported Parts NA Suitable Soil Loamy soil, sandy-loam soil, red soil, clay-mix soils, laterite soil, alluvium-based soils (when not water-logged). Product Attachments 2T blade, 3T blade, 40T Blade, Sawyer, Rotory Power Source battery Performance Parameters Endurance - 1250 hrs+ counting Other Conditions Suitable for inter-cultivation between crop rows, under canopy zones, poultry sheds & farm pathways. Can be operated with minimal training. Lightweight design reduces user fatigue for long-hour field work. Safe to use in villages where fuel storage is difficult — only requires power charging. Minimum cost of product 35000 Product Dimensions 2000X650X450 mm Financing Support open Opportunity Stage Sales Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services yes Engine Details Rated Power: 2 kW electric motor Maximum Speed: 6500 RPM Battery Pack: 48 V, 15 Ah Backup Time: Up to 180 minutes (depending on attachment) Charging Time: 2.5 hours (fast charger optional) Tube Diameter: 28 mm | Shaft Diameter: 8 mm Weight: 11.25 kg Number of Unit Installed 4 Year Launched 2024 Product Weight 12 Kgs Technical Training yes Suitable Terrains Flat lands, gentle slopes, orchard inter-rows, plantation pathways, small & marginal farm plots, terrace farming patches. Spare Parts for Product yes Maximum cost of product 49400 Network Distributors few', '{"innovation_id":"4330","slug":"electric-brush-cutter-e-brush-cutter","title":"Electric Brush Cutter (e-Brush Cutter)","description":"The e-Brush Cutter is a multi-purpose electric agricultural implement designed to replace conventional petrol engine brush cutters with a cleaner, quieter, and more economical solution. It is suitable for daily farm operations including harvesting, weeding, pruning, raking, and landscaping.\nTechnical Specifications:\nRated Power: 2 kW electric motor\nMaximum Speed: 6500 RPM\nBattery Pack: 48 V, 15 Ah\nBackup Time: Up to 180 minutes (depending on attachment)\nCharging Time: 2 hours (fast charger optional)\nTube Diameter: 28 mm | Shaft Diameter: 8 mm\nWeight: 11.25 kg\nPerformance & Operations:\nThe system can perform all operations typically handled by engine-based brush cutters, delivering consistent power with very low vibration and near-silent operation.\nCost & Sustainability:\nOperating cost of approximately &#8377;1.8 - &#8377;2 per hour\nNear-zero maintenance due to absence of fuel, oil, and engine components\nZero emissions and low noise, making it environmentally friendly and safer for operators\nThe e-Brush Cutter is designed for small and marginal farmers seeking a reliable, low-cost, and sustainable alternative to fuel-powered farm equipment.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4330/electric-brush-cutter-e-brush-cutter","organization_name":"Agrilectric Private Limited","organization_code":"AGRIL1764931859632","organization_description":"Agrilectric Private Limited is an agri-technology enterprise focused on developing electric and smart farm mechanization solutions for small and marginal farmers in India. The company aims to reduce farmers'' dependence on fuel-powered equipment by offering low-operating-cost, low-maintenance, and environmentally sustainable alternatives.\nAgrilectric designs and manufactures electric agricultural implements that improve productivity while lowering operational expenses, noise, emissions, and physical fatigue. With a strong focus on affordability, usability, and after-sales support, the enterprise addresses real on-ground challenges faced by farmers across diverse crop systems and terrains.\nThe company''s mission is to make clean, efficient, and accessible farm mechanization available to every farmer, supporting sustainable agriculture and long-term rural impact.","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.MAINTENANCE_AND_MANAGEMENT"],"subcategories":["Maintenance and management"],"tag_codes":["TAG.HARVESTING","TAG.WEEDING"],"tags":["Harvesting","Weeding"],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"35000","maximum_cost":"49400","power_source":"battery","year_launched":"2024","primary_location":"No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India","location_text":"No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India | Karnataka, India","locations":["No.94, Lakshmanappa Layout, Silvepura Post Hessaraghatta Hobli, Yelahanka Taluk North, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560090, India","Karnataka, India"],"latitude":13.1151600552861,"longitude":77.50414697528532,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1766398470911-WhatsApp_Image_2025-11-06_at_22.59.34_fabee34d.jpg","image_urls":["https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1766398470911-WhatsApp_Image_2025-11-06_at_22.59.34_fabee34d.jpg","https://attachment-ms.s