icity consumption\nImproved crop consistency\nReduced labor & travel cost\nBetter irrigation scheduling\nIncreased productivity\nThe solution is suitable for small, marginal, and commercial farmers growing field crops, horticulture crops, and plantations.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4874/heliot-smart-irrigation-controller-motor-control-system","organization_name":"NAVARITI INNOVATION PVT LTD","organization_code":"NAVAR1723445963240","organization_description":"Navariti Innovation Pvt Ltd is a deep-tech startup working at the intersection of AI, IoT, and Climate-Tech. Through its HELIOT.AI brand, the company develops smart farming solutions including Automatic Weather Stations, Smart Irrigation Controllers, Soil Monitoring Devices, and AI-based farm advisory systems.\nFounded by alumni of IIT Bombay and BITS Pilani, Navariti focuses on improving water-use efficiency, crop productivity, and climate resilience for small and marginal farmers.\nThe company partners with FPOs, NGOs, CSR initiatives, agricultural universities, and rural development organizations to scale climate-smart agricultural technologies across India.","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.MAINTENANCE_AND_MANAGEMENT"],"subcategories":["Maintenance and management"],"tag_codes":["TAG.IRRIGATION"],"tags":["Irrigation","IOT based motor automation","Precision agriculture "],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"6999","maximum_cost":"9999","power_source":"Electric (Connected to Pump Line) with Internal Control Circuit Optional Solar-powered variant available","year_launched":"2021","primary_location":"Balanagar, Hyderabad, Telangana, India","location_text":"Balanagar, Hyderabad, Telangana, India | Karnataka, India | Telangana, India | Maharashtra, India | Andhra Pradesh, India","locations":["Balanagar, Hyderabad, Telangana, India","Karnataka, India",