insert into public.innovation_guild_products (portal_product_id, portal_vendor_id, vendor_name, product_name, product_description, product_link, product_image_url, product_gallery_urls, product_video_urls, product_location_text, product_categories, product_subcategories, product_specifications, tags, search_text, raw_product, synced_at, updated_at) values ('5065', 'UNG_A1772518016839', 'UNG Agros', 'JHT-01 Micro Tiller – Redefining Micro Cultivation', 'JHT-01 Micro Tiller - Brush Cutter Engine Based Compact Cultivation Machine
The JHT-01 Micro Tiller is a powerful, compact soil cultivation machine specially designed using a high-performance brush cutter engine, delivering efficient land preparation for small and medium-scale farmers. Built for durability, performance, and easy handling, this innovative micro tiller provides strong torque and smooth operation while remaining lightweight and fuel-efficient.
Designed for inter cultivation, weed control, and soil loosening, the JHT-01 is ideal for vegetable farms, row crops, orchards, nurseries, polyhouse farming, and small agricultural plots where larger machines cannot operate efficiently.
Powerful Brush Cutter Engine Performance
The heart of the JHT-01 Micro Tiller is its reliable brush cutter petrol engine, known for:
High RPM output
Strong torque for deep soil penetration
Fuel efficiency
Easy pull-start mechanism
Low maintenance design
This engine ensures consistent power delivery, allowing the machine to break compact soil, remove weeds, and prepare fine seedbeds with minimal effort.
Compact Yet Heavy-Duty Construction
Despite its compact design, the JHT-01 is built with:
Heavy-duty steel frame
Durable transmission system
Strong rotary blade assembly
Stable traction wheel support
The machine provides excellent balance and control, ensuring smooth field movement without excessive vibration.
Key Features of JHT-01 Micro Tiller
Brush cutter petrol engine powered
Lightweight and easy to handle
Suitable for narrow rows and small plots
Efficient weed removal capability
Excellent soil aeration performance
Low fuel consumption
Farmer-friendly design
Easy maintenance and service
Ideal Applications
The JHT-01 Micro Tiller is perfect for:
&#127793; Vegetable cultivation
&#127806; Inter-row cultivation
&#127807; Weed management
&#127813; Tomato, chilli, brinjal, and row crops
&#127795; Orchard soil loosening
&#127969; nurseries
