ar Launched 2020 Product Attachments Yes Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services yes Power Source Manual Other Conditions None Number of Unit Installed Not listed Weather Conditions Suitable for all weather Demo Installations yes Performance Parameters Crop nutrific value, Soil fertility, Yield etc.', '{"innovation_id":"4241","slug":"jiva-water-farm-device-vipasa-better-water-for-higher-yield-and-soil-fertility","title":"Jiva Water Farm Device Vipasa - Better Water for Higher Yield and Soil Fertility","description":"Vipasa is a non-electric water device, ideal for small agricultural lands, poultry, and cattle farms, designed to improve water efficiency and absorption by roots, stems, and plants. It enhances soil fertility, reduces soil salinity, and boosts crop nutritional value. With better water efficiency, it supports higher yields, faster crop cycles, and improved overall farm productivity. For poultry and cattle, consistent water quality helps maintain optimal health for livestock and supports better productivity. Built with premium-grade stainless steel, Vipasa is durable, low-maintenance, and easy to install for efficient farm irrigation.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4241/jiva-water-farm-device-vipasa-better-water-for-higher-yield-and-soil-fertility","organization_name":"4th Phase Water Technologies Pvt Ltd - Jiva Water","organization_code":"4TH_P1764678674095","organization_description":"At Jiva Water Farm Devices, we believe water isn''t just a means to irrigate - it''s your farm''s most powerful input.But the water reaching your fields today is low in biological activity and less effective for soil and crop health.\nJiva Water Farm Devices are designed to address today''s agricultural challenges, from declining soil health to poor crop quality.\nBy reducing water''s surface tension and enhancing microbial activity, our devices help:\n&#9989; Improve nutrient delivery to plants\n&#9989; Boost soil moisture retention\n&#9989; Reduce salt deposition\n&#9989; Strengthen root-to-fruit development\n&#9989; Support long-term soil health and fertility\nWe''re proud to work alongside progressive farmers across India, helping them grow better with smarter water practices. We''re also grateful to have Murugappa Water Technology and Services (MWTS) as a valuable partner in this journey towards sustainable agriculture.\nBecause in farming, Smart Water = Better Soil = Better Yield.","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.MAINTENANCE_AND_MANAGEMENT"],"subcategories":["Maintenance and management"],"tag_codes":["TAG.IRRIGATION"],"tags":["Irrigation","purification"],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"26950","maximum_cost":"Not listed","power_source":"Manual","year_launched":"2020","primary_location":"4th Phase Water Technologies Pvt Ltd - Jiva Water, 12/2, 2nd Main Rd, below SBI, 7th Block, Jayanagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560070, India","location_text":"4th Phase Water Technologies Pvt Ltd - Jiva Water, 12/2, 2nd Main Rd, below SBI, 7th Block, Jayanagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560070, India | Kerala, India | Maharashtra, India | Telangana, India | Karnataka, India | Odisha, India | Andhra Pradesh, India | Gujarat, India","locations":["4th Phase Water Technologies Pvt Ltd - Jiva Water, 12/2, 2nd Main Rd, below SBI, 7th Block, Jayanagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560070, India","Kerala, India","Maharashtra, India","Telangana, India","Karnataka, India","Odisha, India","Andhra Pradesh, India","Gujarat, India"],"latitude":12.9303665,"longitude":77.57825439999999,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1764768914968-Jiva_edited03.jpg","image_urls":["https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1764768914968-Jiva_edited03.jpg","https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_galler