CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.NUM_OF_UNITS_INSTALLED"},{"key":"Power Source","value":"SOLAR","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.POWER_SOURCE"},{"key":"Imported Parts","value":"NA","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.IMPORTED_PARTS"},{"key":"Product Dimensions","value":"9ft * 4 ft","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PRODUCT_DIMENSIONS"},{"key":"Product Attachments","value":"Solar Panel, Charge Controller and Battery","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PRODUCT_ATTACHMENTS"},{"key":"Year Launched","value":"2014","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.YEAR_LAUNCHED"}]'::jsonb, '{"Drying"}', 'Mini Solar Mobile Dryer Grain shell Solar Mobile Dryer (SMD2000/SMD4000) is a collapsible, tunnel type dryer with 2 ton (2000Kg)/4 ton (4000kg) drying capacity designed to protect the agricultural commodity from uneven / sudden rains during drying, and to prevent spillage and contamination damage. Drying efficiency is dependent on the solar radiation, relative humidity of the ambient air, and moisture content of concerned agricultural commodity. The Solar Mobile Dryer consists of semi-transparent cover made of UV Resistant Poly film/cross laminated film connected to the black fabric coated PVC film by a high strength zipper. Through the semi-transparent top cover, solar radiation enters the drying chamber and heats of the agricultural commodity being dried. Moisture in the commodity is evaporated and pushed by the DC Fans out from the drying chamber. The Solar Mobile Dryer SMD2000/SMD4000 drying possible even during unexpected rain conditions. It can dry grains, seeds, nuts, coffee beans, Cocoa beans, spices, oil seeds at an average drying rate of 0.5 to 1.0% per hour on grains. However, during full sunny condition drying time is about 24 hours on a moisture content reduce 28 to 14%. Grain Shell Drying Agriculture Processing A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India Telangana, India Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services yes Demo Installations yes Suitable Crops All Crops Suitable Soil All Soils Opportunity Stage Sales Minimum cost of product 15000 Suitable Terrains All Terrains Other Conditions NA Weather Conditions Works effectively in bright sunny days Performance Parameters Tested for drying of Chilli (Moisture content) Engine Details 18 ah Battery Spare Parts for Product yes Maximum cost of product 25000 Technical Training yes Network Distributors none Product Weight 15 kg Financing Support no Number of Unit Installed 5 Power Source SOLAR Imported Parts NA Product Dimensions 9ft * 4 ft Product Attachments Solar Panel, Charge Controller and Battery Year Launched 2014', '{"innovation_id":"5187","slug":"mini-solar-mobile-dryer","title":"Mini Solar Mobile Dryer","description":"Grain shell Solar Mobile Dryer (SMD2000/SMD4000) is a collapsible, tunnel type dryer with 2 ton (2000Kg)/4 ton (4000kg) drying capacity designed to protect the agricultural commodity from uneven / sudden rains during drying, and to prevent spillage and contamination damage. Drying efficiency is dependent on the solar radiation, relative humidity of the ambient air, and moisture content of concerned agricultural commodity. The Solar Mobile Dryer consists of semi-transparent cover made of UV Resistant Poly film/cross laminated film connected to the black fabric coated PVC film by a high strength zipper. Through the semi-transparent top cover, solar radiation enters the drying chamber and heats of the agricultural commodity being dried. Moisture in the commodity is evaporated and pushed by the DC Fans out from the drying chamber. The Solar Mobile Dryer SMD2000/SMD4000 drying possible even during unexpected rain conditions. It can dry grains, seeds, nuts, coffee beans, Cocoa beans, spices, oil seeds at an average drying rate of 0.5 to 1.0% per hour on grains. However, during full sunny condition drying time is about 24 hours on a moisture content reduce 28 to 14%.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/5187/mini-solar-mobile-dryer","organization_name":"Grain Shell","organization_code":"GRAIN1762252229351","organization_description":"Grain Shell is a leading innovator in agricultural storage and drying solutions, committed to addressing the critical challenges of post-harvest losses through sustainable technologies. Based in Hyderabad, India, we specialize in eco-friendly products powered by solar energy, aimed at improving the quality and longevity of agricultural commodities. Our solutions are designed with small-scale farmers in mind, helping them preserve crops, reduce waste, and maximize profitability while promoting environmental preservation. With a strong emphasis on green technology, our range of solar dryers, airtight storage bags and hermetic storage cubicles are engineered to deliver cost-effective and efficient solutions for drying and storing grains, fruits, vegetables, and other agricultural products. By empowering farmers to adopt better storage practices, we contribute to enhancing food security and ensuring that post-harvest losses are minimized.","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.PROCESSING"],"subcategories":["Processing"],"tag_codes":["TAG.DRYING"],"tags":["Drying"],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"15000","maximum_cost":"25000","power_source":"SOLAR","year_launched":"2014","primary_location":"A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India","location_text":"A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India | Telangana, India","locations":["A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India","Telangana, India"],"latitude":17.4784775,"longitude":78.5506371,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1774331891029-Mini_Solar_dryer.jpeg","image_urls":["https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1774331891029-Mini_Solar_dryer.jpeg","https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/177433