h, India Opportunity Stage Sales Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services yes Suitable Terrains All Terrains Spare Parts for Product yes Weather Conditions Suitable for all weather conditions but effectively works in Sunny days. Financing Support no Product Dimensions 50 * 10 ft Demo Installations yes Number of Unit Installed 5 Suitable Crops All Crops Technical Training yes Power Source Solar Operated Performance Parameters Drying capacity in per hour Product Weight 80-100 kg Minimum cost of product 100000 Other Conditions NA Suitable Soil All Soils Maximum cost of product Not listed Network Distributors none Year Launched 2020 Engine Details 180 Watts Imported Parts NA Product Attachments Battery and Solar Panel', '{"innovation_id":"4823","slug":"solar-mobile-dryer","title":"Solar Mobile Dryer","description":"Grain shell Solar Mobile Dryer (SMD2000/SMD4000) is a collapsible, tunnel type dryer with 2 ton (2000Kg)/4 ton (4000kg) drying capacity designed to protect the agricultural commodity from uneven / sudden rains during drying, and to prevent spillage and contamination damage. Drying efficiency is dependent on the solar radiation, relative humidity of the ambient air, and moisture content of concerned agricultural commodity. The Solar Mobile Dryer consists of semi-transparent cover made of UV Resistant Poly film/cross laminated film connected to the black fabric coated PVC film by a high strength zipper. Through the semi-transparent top cover, solar radiation enters the drying chamber and heats of the agricultural commodity being dried. Moisture in the commodity is evaporated and pushed by the DC Fans out from the drying chamber. The Solar Mobile Dryer SMD2000/SMD4000 drying possible even during unexpected rain conditions. It can dry grains, seeds, nuts, coffee beans, Cocoa beans, spices, oil seeds at an average drying rate of 0.5 to 1.0% per hour on grains. However, during full sunny condition drying time is about 24 hours on a moisture content reduce 28 to 14%.","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/4823/solar-mobile-dryer","organization_name":"Grain Shell","organization_code":"GRAIN1762252229351","organization_description":"Grain Shell is a leading innovator in agricultural storage and drying solutions, committed to addressing the critical challenges of post-harvest losses through sustainable technologies. Based in Hyderabad, India, we specialize in eco-friendly products powered by solar energy, aimed at improving the quality and longevity of agricultural commodities. Our solutions are designed with small-scale farmers in mind, helping them preserve crops, reduce waste, and maximize profitability while promoting environmental preservation. With a strong emphasis on green technology, our range of solar dryers, airtight storage bags and hermetic storage cubicles are engineered to deliver cost-effective and efficient solutions for drying and storing grains, fruits, vegetables, and other agricultural products. By empowering farmers to adopt better storage practices, we contribute to enhancing food security and ensuring that post-harvest losses are minimized.","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.PROCESSING"],"subcategories":["Processing"],"tag_codes":[],"tags":["Drying"],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"100000","maximum_cost":"Not listed","power_source":"Solar Operated","year_launched":"2020","primary_location":"A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India","location_text":"A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India | Telangana, India | Andhra Pradesh, India","locations":["A. S. Rao Nagar, Secunderabad, Telangana, India","Telangana, India","Andhra Pradesh, India"],"latitude":17.4784775,"longitude":78.5506371,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1770796921283-service-3.jpg","image_urls":["https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1770796921283-service-3.jpg","https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1770796921338-service-4.jpg"],"videos":[{"source_url":"https://youtu.be/1Dgl7J64OU0","embed_url":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1Dgl7J64OU0","platform":"youtube"},{"source_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1770796923789-VID-20251029-WA0016.mp4","embed_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_gallery/1770796923789-VID-20251029-WA0016.mp4","platform":"video"}],"specifications":[{"key":"Opportunity Stage","value":"Sales","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.OPPORTUNITY_STAGE"},{"key":"Training on Maintenance and After Sales Services","value":"yes","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.TRAINING_ON_MAINTENANCE_AND_AFTER_SALES_SERVICES"},{"key":"Suitable Terrains","value":"All Terrains","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.SUITABLE_TERRAINS"},{"key":"Spare Parts for Product","value":"yes","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.SPARE_PARTS_FOR_PRODUCT"},{"key":"Weather Conditions","value":"Suitable for all weather conditions but effectively works in Sunny days.","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.WEATHER_CONDITIONS"},{"key":"Financing Support","value":"no","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.FINANCING_SUPPORT"},{"key":"Product Dimensions","value":"50 * 10 ft","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PRODUCT_DIMENSIONS"},{"key":"Demo Installations","value":"yes","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.DEMO_INSTALLATIONS"},{"key":"Number of Unit Installed","value":"5","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.NUM_OF_UNITS_INSTALLED"},{"key":"Suitable Crops","value":"All Crops","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.SUITABLE_CROPS"},{"key":"Technical Training","value":"yes","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.TECHNICAL_TRAINING"},{"key":"Power Source","value":"Solar Operated","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.POWER_SOURCE"},{"key":"Performance Parameters","value":"Drying capacity in per hour","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PERFORMANCE_PARAMETERS"},{"key":"Product Weight","value":"80-100 kg","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PRODUCT_WEIGHT"},{"key":"Minimum cost of product","value":"100000","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.MINIMUM_COST_OF_PRODUCT"},{"key":"Other Conditions","value":"NA","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.OTHER_CONDITIONS"},{"key":"Suitable Soil","value":"All Soils","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.SUITABLE_SOIL"},{"key":"Maximum cost of product","value":"Not listed","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.MAXIMUM_COST_OF_PRODUCT"},{"key":"Network Distributors","value":"none","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.NETWORK_DISTRIBUTORS"},{"key":"Year Launched","value":"2020","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.YEAR_LAUNCHED"},{"key":"Engine Details","value":"180 Watts","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.ENGINE_DETAILS"},{"key":"Imported Parts","value":"NA","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.IMPORTED_PARTS"},{"key":"Product Attachments","value":"Battery and Solar Panel","code":"CHANGEMAKER_META_CODE.PRODUCT_ATTACHMENTS"}],"created_at":"2026-02-11T13:46:26.361+05:30"}'::jsonb, now(), now());
insert into public.innovation_guild_products (portal_product_id, portal_vendor_id, vendor_name, product_name, product_description, product_link, product_image_url, product_gallery_urls, product_video_urls, product_location_text, product_categories, product_subcategories, product_specifications, tags, search_text, raw_product, synced_at, updated_at) values ('1349', 'RURAL1723444073604', 'Rural Rise Agrinery LLP', 'Sowing Tool', 'Description: The Seed Sowing Tool is an ergonomically designed agricultural implement that facilitates the efficient sowing of seeds. This innovative tool allows farmers to plant seeds while standing upright, thereby minimizing spinal stress and enhancing overall planting efficiency.
Ergonomic Design
Standing Operation: Enables farmers to sow seeds without bending, reducing the risk of back injuries and fatigue.
Comfort Grip: Handles designed for prolonged use without causing discomfort.
Ease of Use
Seed Funnel: A funnel at the top of the tool for easy seed loading.
Simple Operation: Intuitive design that requires minimal training for effective use.
Efficiency
Sharp Pipe End: The main structure includes a sharp end that easily penetrates tilled soil, facilitating quick and smooth planting.
Reduced Labor: Speeds up the sowing process, saving time and effort.
Equidistant Sowing
Guide Attachment: Ensures seeds are planted at consistent intervals, promoting uniform growth and optimal use of space.
Materials
Main Body: Durable, lightweight metal or high-strength plastic to withstand field conditions.
Sharp End: Hardened metal for easy soil penetration.
Handles: Rubberized or cushioned grips for comfort.
Dimensions (approximate):
Length: 1.5 meters (adjustable to suit different user heights).
Weight: 2-3 kilograms for easy maneuverability.
Applications
Crops: Suitable for a variety of small to medium-sized seeds such as grains, legumes, and vegetables.
Field Types: Effective in various types of tilled soil.
Benefits:
Health: Reduces the physical strain on farmers, potentially lowering medical costs and improving quality of life.
Productivity: Increases planting speed and efficiency, allowing more ground to be covered in less time.
Yield: Promotes uniform crop growth, which can lead to higher yields and better-quality produce.
Maintenance
Cleaning: Regular cleaning recommended to prevent seed blockage and ensure smooth operation.
Storage: Store in a dry place to prevent rust and wear.
Price Range: Varies depending on material and additional features, typically ranging from
