elivers sharp cutting performance and long-lasting durability. The 9-inch width makes it ideal for medium to wide row spacing crops, enabling farmers and gardeners to remove weeds quickly without damaging surrounding plants.\nThe strong welded frame and sturdy handle socket ensure stability during operation. Its balanced design reduces user fatigue, making it suitable for extended use in farms, orchards, vegetable gardens, and nurseries.\nThis tool not only removes unwanted weeds but also improves soil aeration and moisture penetration, promoting healthier root growth and better crop productivity.\nWhether used in open fields or garden beds, the Trapezoid Hoe - 9 Inch offers reliability, strength, and efficient performance for daily agricultural operations.\n&#9989; Key Benefits\nWide 9-inch cutting edge for faster coverage\nDurable carbon steel construction\nStrong and stable frame design\nSuitable for agriculture & gardening\nHelps improve soil aeration\nIdeal for medium to loose soil types","detail_url":"https://innovationguild.in/innovation/5071/trapezoide-hoe-9-inch","organization_name":"UNG Agros","organization_code":"UNG_A1772518016839","organization_description":"","tenant_name":"Innovation Guild","category_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.AGRI"],"categories":["Agriculture"],"subcategory_codes":["OPPORTUNITY_SUB_CATEGORY_INNOVATORS.PRODUCTION"],"subcategories":["Production"],"tag_codes":["TAG.WEEDING"],"tags":["Weeding"],"stage":"Sales","minimum_cost":"1000","maximum_cost":"Not listed","power_source":"Manual","year_launched":"2017","primary_location":"#32, 1st main, 2nd cross, Muneshwara layout, Laggere, Bengaluru - 560058","location_text":"#32, 1st main, 2nd cross, Muneshwara layout, Laggere, Bengaluru - 560058 | Karnataka, India","locations":["#32, 1st main, 2nd cross, Muneshwara layout, Laggere, Bengaluru - 560058","Karnataka, India"],"latitude":0,"longitude":0,"cover_image_url":"https://attachment-ms.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/1804/opportunity_g